# Currency Exchange Service

This service provides an API to get the current USD to UAH exchange rate and to subscribe to email notifications about the exchange rate.

## API Endpoints

### GET /api/rate
Returns the current USD to UAH exchange rate.

### POST /api/subscribe
Subscribes an email address to daily notifications about the exchange rate.

Request body:
```json
{
    "email": "example@example.com"
}
